           move      0200                 to   d-sld-mag-tip-sld      .
           move      rr-dat-sit           to   d-sld-mag-dat-sld      .
           move      "U"                  to   d-sld-mag-uot-dpz      .
           move      rr-dpz-inu           to   d-sld-mag-cod-dpz      .
           move      kk0-tip-mag          to   d-sld-mag-tip-mag      .
           move      kk0-num-mag          to   d-sld-mag-num-mag      .
           move      "T"                  to   d-sld-mag-uot-var      .
           move      spaces               to   d-sld-mag-var-mag      .
           move      "U"                  to   d-sld-mag-uot-ctm      .
           move      kk0-cod-ctm          to   d-sld-mag-cod-ctm      .
           move      kk0-tip-arc          to   d-sld-mag-tip-arc      .
           move      "U"                  to   d-sld-mag-uot-arc      .
           move      kk0-cod-arc          to   d-sld-mag-cod-arc      .
           move      "U"                  to   d-sld-mag-uot-dpa      .
           move      kk0-dpz-arc          to   d-sld-mag-dpz-arc      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Richiamo del sottoprogramma             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   det-sld-mag-cll-000  thru det-sld-mag-cll-999    .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Selezione                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rr-snx-zer           =    01 and
                     d-sld-mag-sld-mag    =    zero
                     go to prn-sel-rec-900.
           if        rr-snx-zer           =    02 and
                     d-sld-mag-sld-mag    not  < zero
                     go to prn-sel-rec-900.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Aggiornamento totale dipendenze         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      d-sld-mag-sld-mag    to   w-sdp-tot-dpz          .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Uscita per selezione superata           *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-sel-rec-999.
       prn-sel-rec-900.
